Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:52.06,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}假面的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌  是我们学校的学生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架了吗  真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这个世界里时间没有动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还真是悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:03:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}入此门者  当抛弃一切希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:03:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎各位同学来到小生广原雪子担当部长的考现学部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考现学就是以现代社会的森罗万象为对象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做调查  研究的学问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说就是考古学的现代版
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我已经听了好几遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了  考现学部终于盼来了新部员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是两名女生和一名男生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的  姐姐在七年前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在赤夜里看到的肯定是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡思乱想太多比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经和大家聚到一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴啊  认识了好多伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子真厉害啊  在赤夜中一个人生存下来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  雪子也有特别的能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一生气就很可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子总是这么活泼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为也就只有这点优点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  在哪跟谁打架能伤成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的出勤快不够了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近总是旷课  还想不想升学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦  你这嫁不出去的缺男人婆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久  你的对女性不出手主义让我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  给我站住贤久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士称呼我们为「碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要回答即将消失的「碎片」们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「碎片」是指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及「碎片」还有几人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还知道一个人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在赤夜刚开始那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被个好像正义的伙伴一样的人救了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子同学  你也认识她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「她」  是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说得出口啊  那个世界的事  还有这能力的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  决定了  今天的活动就是寻找那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然决定了那就事不宜迟  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久  逃哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千钧一发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然撞进来干什么  太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是正义的伙伴先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜妹  又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同学  搜查活动结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人吃惊啊  能看到黑月的人竟然有这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像叫皐月来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的什么能力都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你这样还能活到今天啊  真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别生气嘛  我是在夸奖你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来点薯条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样啊  谁也不清楚赤夜的详细情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  田岛贤久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不进考现学部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越弱的狗就越想聚到一窝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田岛贤久  对团体没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说我们是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是赤夜再临的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会自己想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没礼貌的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  看起来虽然是那样  不过他是个挺温柔的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会恶心呢  反而会让大家感到羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱前辈  乱打一通是赢不了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是急躁刀路就会越乱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为何而战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护结花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听上去真可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是嘴上功夫  身体却跟不上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的感情没有转换成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你握着的剑寄宿着觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟就是达到悟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的感情还没有达到悟的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要训练的不是身体而是心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将感情转换成力量  只需要考虑这点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将感情转换成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到力量  能保护结花的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  我到底在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说出来很尴尬  不过刚才要是在战斗中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说保护结花  驱前辈都已经死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我太直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了试试驱的觉悟  我本想对她攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才他的动作是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  结花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我还是弱得很丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一定会保护好结花的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉强  我也一样没有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要驱君能在我身边就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这也是为了我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护结花  想把这份感情转换成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey ciao,buongiorno shiori
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}你好  早上好  小栞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Piacere,come sta shiori?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}很高兴见到你  小栞你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quanto costa？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你别用这种让人不堪入耳的意大利语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想跟拉丁的热血沸腾的归国子女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一场火热的双语恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你烧尽吧  烧成灰为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,capito
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}噢  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小栞  在欧美是女士优先的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都愿意听你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请顺着这条路一直往前走  在右转的地方去死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  乐意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右转
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carbonara
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}卡波那拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}注：一种美食
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arrivederci  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(295,325)\fs21}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个超级笨蛋  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再笨下去我都不知道该说他什么笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花已经先过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱同学  有关昨天的修行…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  现在正好在做考现学的实际操作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考现学的  实际操作？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  探索为什么结花明明是幼儿体型胸部却这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不下垂也不上挺  不用塑形胸罩就这样还真是现代奇迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在神圣的学园里干这种羞人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  雪子  住手  快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是贤久前辈在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我烧成灰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久前辈是念力点火能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pyrokineticist
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fs21}操焰者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「碎片」们  今夜不会失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对即将变为残骸的罪人们  我没什么好说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无话好说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子同学  他们俩拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铇切长光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙  是用拳法的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快  草壁前辈被压制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  阿瓦利提亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能打倒古拉  这些「碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须担心  这次由伊拉和因威迪亚上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有我斯佩尔比亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  前辈怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美铃前辈  不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我有力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想力量并非所有人都是期望得到才得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫去获取力量  我就是这种境遇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…雪子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这神速…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惊人的战斗能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个小丫头  敢小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛就像换了个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因威迪亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来以为「碎片」的处置交给伊拉就足够了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我统统去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义的伙伴  登场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸…竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤夜要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这代价很重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再见的时候  一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  结花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱…驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  明明受了那么重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞砸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一摘下眼镜就会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双重人格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人般的战斗能力和强劲的杀气  那是在哪学到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊  我不太想说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  雪子  你的伤没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我会再生的  天生死不了的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我很恶心对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我习惯了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前开始大家就都觉得我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生在德拉斯贝尼亚这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是战乱和杀戮之地…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能接受我的人一共有四个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们各位  还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.47,0:22:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会恶心呢  反而会让大家感到羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为就算受伤了也能立刻恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复成原来的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  结花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.57,0:22:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱前辈  美铃前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.08,0:22:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待着你的入部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.57,0:24:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.62,0:24:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.97,0:24:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在噩梦的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.65,0:24:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有答案吗


